Text: Thank you :)  For real thank god for pickles! Without them and sugar snap peas I don't know what I would do.

Author: WastingMyYoungYears
Text: I know that feeling. I assume the calories on pickle jars are for the SMALLEST sized pickles in the jar and the big ones I double the calories on. :( I am so sorry stranger, I can empathize. Still, thank GOD for low calorie, deliciousness of pickles
